PC Number Date Chapter Bill Dept
 2023-02022023-03-09PS
ActFirearms Act
SubjectOrder Authorizing Contribution Agreements with the Provinces
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Public Safety and Emergency Preparedness to ENTER INTO AN AGREEMENT with the government of any province that elects to administer the Act in its jurisdiction on behalf of the federal government for PAYMENT OF COMPENSATION in respect of administrative costs actually incurred by the province in relation to processing licenses, authorizations and applications for licenses and authorizations under the Act.
